  "title": "BD Executive/Manager",
  "description": "<p>Vanshi Global is a diversified innovative software company, specializing in providing a range of cutting-edge technological solutions.  These solutions encompass instant messaging, social platform development, virtual private (VPN) service, blockchain applications, SaaS services, and cloud server proxy services.</p><p><strong>Roles and Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Develop a growth strategy focused both on financial gain and customer satisfaction</li><li>Conduct research to identify customer needs</li><li>Arrange business meetings with prospective clients</li><li>Promote the company’s products/services addressing or predicting clients’ objectives</li><li>Prepare sales contracts ensuring adherence to law-established rules and guidelines</li><li>Keep records of sales, revenue, invoices etc.</li><li>Provide trustworthy feedback and after-sales support</li><li>Build long-term relationships with new and existing customers</li><li>Develop entry level staff into valuable salespeople</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Proficiency in MS office or any other enterprise collaboration platform</li><li>Able to communicate fluently in <strong>both </strong>English and Mandarin as the role is required to communicate professionally to both English and Mandarin speaking counterparts and clients</li><li>Communication and negotiation skills</li><li>Ability to build rapport</li><li>Time management and planning skills</li><li>BSc/BA in business administration, marketing & sales or relevant field</li><li><strong>Proven sales track record or proven working experience as a business development manager, sales executive or a relevant role is a plus</strong></li><li>Meticulous and attention-to-detail</li></ul>",
